{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"categories":1,"event_categories":27},[2,9,15,21],{"id":3,"attributes":4},1,{"slug":5,"name":6,"description":7,"createdAt":8,"updatedAt":8},"nutrition","營養隨筆",null,"2023-02-12T02:39:02.691Z",{"id":10,"attributes":11},2,{"slug":12,"name":13,"description":7,"createdAt":14,"updatedAt":14},"reflection","感悟隨筆","2023-02-12T02:39:02.692Z",{"id":16,"attributes":17},3,{"slug":18,"name":19,"description":7,"createdAt":20,"updatedAt":20},"fitness","運動筆記","2023-02-12T02:39:02.697Z",{"id":22,"attributes":23},4,{"slug":24,"name":25,"description":7,"createdAt":26,"updatedAt":26},"spiritual","心靈勵志","2023-02-12T02:39:02.698Z",[28,33,38,43,47,52],{"id":3,"attributes":29},{"name":30,"slug":31,"description":7,"createdAt":32,"updatedAt":32},"讀書會","book-sharing","2023-02-12T02:38:55.939Z",{"id":16,"attributes":34},{"name":35,"slug":36,"description":7,"createdAt":37,"updatedAt":37},"文化導賞","cultural","2023-02-12T02:38:55.943Z",{"id":22,"attributes":39},{"name":40,"slug":41,"description":7,"createdAt":42,"updatedAt":42},"遊山玩水","hiking","2023-02-12T02:38:55.946Z",{"id":44,"attributes":45},5,{"name":46,"slug":18,"description":7,"createdAt":42,"updatedAt":42},"健體運動",{"id":48,"attributes":49},6,{"name":50,"slug":5,"description":7,"createdAt":51,"updatedAt":51},"活學營養","2023-02-12T02:38:55.947Z",{"id":10,"attributes":53},{"name":54,"slug":55,"description":7,"createdAt":56,"updatedAt":57},"名人面對面","be-our-guest","2023-02-12T02:38:55.942Z","2023-03-08T13:16:12.875Z"],"uses":{"dependencies":["http://127.0.0.1:1337/api/categories?","http://127.0.0.1:1337/api/event-categories?"]},"slash":"always"},{"type":"data","data":[{"id":1,"attributes":2},171,{"title":3,"excerpt":4,"content":5,"slug":6,"createdAt":7,"updatedAt":7,"author":8,"categories":9,"tags":17,"image":39,"related_posts":40},"清肝利膽",null,"\n\n中年以後，膽管系統容易結石😖；根據所處位置，分為肝內膽管結石、總膽管結石及膽囊結石。\n\n膽管系統將肝細胞產生的膽汁，藉由管狀結構輸送至十二指腸，幫助食物消化。膽汁中的膽汁酸、卵磷脂及膽固醇必需保持一定的比例，才能維持膽汁液體的穩定性。當膽汁酸及卵磷脂減少而膽固醇增加時，膽固醇被沉澱析出，慢慢累積而形成結石😱。喝水不足，口味偏濃，食無定時，不吃早餐，飲食過量，尤其是糖、脂肪（特別是反式脂肪）吃得太多，皆是原因。飯後容易脹氣者，較大機會肝膽已有結石🙈。\n\n蛋白質是肝細胞再生的必需成分，且防止脂肪在肝內堆積；惟蛋白質在體內會產生氨氣，若肝功能下降，無法有效代謝氨氣，會傷肝及其他器官，所以必需選擇優質蛋白質😉。此外，維他命B是護肝的主要營養素：B1分解糖分，B2代謝脂肪，B6促進糖分、脂肪及蛋白質的代謝，膽素和肌醇能將多餘脂肪帶離肝臟。米飯可選擇以糙米取代部分白米，多加補充維他命B。\n\n本周日【活學營養：肝膽排毒】將進一步解構肝膽結石的種類與成因，並講解具五千年歴史的肝膽排毒DIY古方，萬勿錯過！💪🏻🤗請發訊息給我們獲取相關資訊及連結。","post200523","2020-05-23T00:00:00.000Z",{"data":4},{"data":10},[11],{"id":12,"attributes":13},1,{"slug":14,"name":15,"description":4,"createdAt":16,"updatedAt":16},"nutrition","營養隨筆","2023-02-12T02:39:02.691Z",{"data":18},[19,24,29,34],{"id":20,"attributes":21},179,{"name":22,"createdAt":23,"updatedAt":23},"膽結石","2023-02-12T03:32:01.371Z",{"id":25,"attributes":26},144,{"name":27,"createdAt":28,"updatedAt":28},"蛋白質","2023-02-12T03:32:01.351Z",{"id":30,"attributes":31},170,{"name":32,"createdAt":33,"updatedAt":33},"肝","2023-02-12T03:32:01.367Z",{"id":35,"attributes":36},167,{"name":37,"createdAt":38,"updatedAt":38},"維他命B","2023-02-12T03:32:01.366Z",{"data":4},{"data":41},[]],"uses":{"dependencies":["http://127.0.0.1:1337/api/posts?populate[author]=true&populate[categories]=true&populate[tags]=true&populate[image]=true&populate[related_posts]=true&filters[slug][$eq]=post200523"],"params":["slug"]}}]}